                {
                    "title": "Executive Director Emeritus",
                    "description": "I provided overall visionary leadership of the Cornell Institute for Climate Smart Solutions (CICSS). This included staffing, programing, and execution of CICSS’s mission, which was to build stakeholder capacity and work toward a future where agricultural, environmental, and social systems are resilient in the face of a rapidly changing climate. In this role I helped raise the profile of climate change and how CICSS and Cornell are positioned to respond to this challenge given the depth and breadth of the expertise among the faculty and programs. I helped to ensure that Cornell is recognized and rewarded for being the global leader in climate change and its impact on agriculture and the food system.\n",
                    "locationName": "Ithaca, New York Area",
